title: IAA Tonight | Pro Football Hall of Famer Rod Woodson AND L.A. Rams Season Preview
description: I AM ATHLETE got the chance to speak to Pro Football Hall of Famer Rod Woodson. Tune in to find out what hIs thoughts are on the Hall of Fame selection process. Plus, we preview the Los Angeles Rams 2022 season. Will they repeat as Super Bowl Champs if Matt Stafford isn't fully healthy?
author: smanderville@houseofathlete.com (Leger Douzable, Chantel Tremetiere, LeSean Mccoy, Brandon Marshall)
